name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: fs.s3a.threads.keepalivetime
description:
Number of seconds a thread can be idle before being
    terminated.

name: dfs.namenode.blockreport.max.lock.hold.time
description: The BlockReportProcessingThread max write lock hold time in ms.

name: mapreduce.task.timeout
description:
The number of milliseconds before a task will be
  terminated if it neither reads an input, writes an output, nor
  updates its status string.  A value of 0 disables the timeout.

name: dfs.namenode.edit.log.autoroll.check.interval.ms
description:
How often an active namenode will check if it needs to roll its edit log,
    in milliseconds.

name: dfs.short.circuit.shared.memory.watcher.interrupt.check.ms
description:
The length of time in milliseconds that the short-circuit shared memory
    watcher will go between checking for java interruptions sent from other
    threads.  This is provided mainly for unit tests.

name: yarn.app.mapreduce.am.container.log.limit.kb
description:
The maximum size of the MRAppMaster attempt container logs in KB.
    0 disables the cap.
